record.title: CORRECTION TO JOURNAL OF PROCEEDINGS
record.narrative:
CORRECTION TO JOURNAL OF PROCEEDINGS -- (Senate - July 19, 2007)

[Page: S9643]

speaking.paragraph: Madam President, I ask unanimous consent that the Journal of proceedings be corrected to conform to the earlier agreement to vitiate the vote relative to amendment No. 2356.

record.chair: Without objection, it is so ordered.
